metadata.description:
I can talk about my madness here, now, and until you get bored and start playing with your greasy hair. My precious madness that I have just accepted, embraced, and have no intention of letting go. I can talk at length about what he added to me and lost my loved ones. But how long that will be is up to you because I don't want to take your time, to leave a black mark on your "bright" minds by talking about my own darkness of mind.

June, 2023
by Demon Ego
metadata.name: I Finally Admitted My Insanity #1/9
